---
title: Garlic Prawns & Bacon Fried Rice with Garlicky Greens & Pickled Cucumber
description: If you’re in the mood for a good fried rice with prawns, do we have the answer for you! The prawns are coated in sweet soy
flavours, and seared in the pan to really make them pop with the crispy bacon bites tossed through golden fried rice. It’s the
perfect way to satisfy that craving.
